UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1910
1 requirements in subparagraph 1. of this paragraph or complete an
2 eligible program of study, the eligible student shall be subject to
3 subsections (6) and (8) of this section.
4 Section 2. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of
5 $4,175,000 in each fiscal year of the 2026-2028 fiscal biennium to the Kentucky Higher
6 Education Assistance Authority for the scholarship pilot program established in
7 subsection (13) of Section 1 of this Act.
8 Section 3. Whereas the scholarship pilot program established in this Act begins
9 with the 2026-2027 academic year, and immediate planning and preparation are required
10 for timely implementation of the program, an emergency is declared to exist, and this Act
11 takes effect upon its passage and approval by the Governor or upon its otherwise
12 becoming a law.
